{"tid":2377277,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有個好耐冇見嘅朋友叫我讀HKUE","createTime":"2021-01-23T12:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T10:47:46.000Z","uid":87778,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb91c8d3da2ef1e3a6b6587bbd899e29d6524dd","tid":2377277,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"話有證書可以揾份好工 信唔信佢好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35515ea420b7df334b75840443df617b027592c","tid":2377277,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"做下線<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf32d8ce843c360ab391262a7dc6ec345de1bf34","tid":2377277,"uid":230641,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"提到HKUE的請絕交"},{"pid":"f435e1fb70eaae2a44f3024d35286fea3f51f1a0","tid":2377277,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"間野評價好差架？咩係下線？"},{"pid":"39a34ce583e27e56ba7e70b922a7530fc4ebcb29","tid":2377277,"uid":344896,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"間嘢好似冇資歷架構㗎<br />\n識人係個度讀咗1x個degree<br />\n我聽完笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f2fc96c2aa571237788d365232c03476e39ee8","tid":2377277,"uid":307514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"咪撚咁蠢啦"},{"pid":"24d1b5acc948824fa9e46301b28acac8597767ae","tid":2377277,"uid":83016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"你應該兜巴打醒個死傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後絕交<br />\n千其唔好信佢"},{"pid":"dddb3b6524b4bbc19a3e99e309454e3a6ea03204","tid":2377277,"uid":7828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=e2ddd6ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=11df106f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=188ddc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}